ar experience while giving beer-lovers the opportunity to enjoy their favourite Tiger Beer and other Nigerian Breweries brands. Vanguard Nigerian Breweries  NB  Plc, has finally launched in Nigeria the Tiger Beer brand from Singapore. May 2, 2018 In "Business" On Saturday, December 29th Tiger beer kicked off the “Uncage Series” by hosting the biggest niche party of the year. The brand uncaged the arts at the beautifully tucked away treasure that is the African Artists Foundation, Victoria Island, Lagos featuring some of Nigeria’s budding talents and influential personalities from… January 12, 2019 In "Entertainment" Guinness Gold, the new premium lager beer, thrilled celebrities, media icons, media influencers and consumers as Guinness Nigeria Plc treated Nigerians to a one-of-a-kind immersion at the Landmark Centre, Lagos. Guests were immersed in a great night of rich flavours, fine foods, great music, hi-tech audio visual sensory experience, all… April 10, 2019 In "News"